Specify tha x n' y coordinates where you want tha point drawn.
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.ZN XDrawPoint
function uses tha foreground pixel n' function componentz of the
GC ta draw a single point tha fuck into tha specified drawable; 
.ZN XDrawPoints
draws multiple points dis way.
.ZN CoordModeOrigin
treats all coordinates as relatizzle ta tha origin,
and
.ZN CoordModePrevious
treats all coordinates afta tha straight-up original gangsta as relatizzle ta tha previous point.
.ZN XDrawPoints
draws tha points up in tha order listed up in tha array.
.LP
Both functions use these GC components: function, plane-mask,
foreground, subwindow-mode, clip-x-origin, clip-y-origin, n' clip-mask.
.LP
.ZN XDrawPoint
can generate
.ZN BadDrawable ,
.ZN BadGC ,
and 
.ZN BadMatch 
errors.
.ZN XDrawPoints
can generate
.ZN BadDrawable ,
.ZN BadGC ,
.ZN BadMatch ,
and
.ZN BadValue 
errors.
.SH STRUCTURES
